s[566] = "SqlitePassDbo.TSqlitePassDataset.OnMasterChanged^SqlitePassDbo.TSqlitePassDataset.html#OnMasterChanged^<code>OnMasterChanged</code> is triggered when <a class=\"normal\"  href=\"SqlitePassDbo.TSqlitePassDataset.html#MasterSource\">MasterSource</a> records changes (scroll, data changes, etc...).^ The concerned field is send as parameter to the event handler. ^0"
